{"tid":1814624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Openrice戰線] 用OpenRice令到普通人都唔會食藍店","createTime":"2020-01-07T03:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T03:51:37.000Z","uid":61886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee7a69d6e3f92501e1f6c8a897f6ce6dfd12754","tid":1814624,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:43:47.000Z","msg":"你哋知唔知點解藍店仲會咁多人食<br />\n<br />\n因為好多港豬根本唔理黃定藍<br />\n見openrice幾好好評就會去食<br />\n<br />\n所以我地一定要谷起黃店好評<br />\n同埋藍店負評<br />\n<br />\n舉個例子<br />\n<br />\n四川辣妹子<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNfRHBn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNfRHBn.png&h=38e3b3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0KdS200~dj3NH0yhv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0KdS200~dj3NH0yhv&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=7e24f3b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0KdS200~dj3NH0yhv</a><br />\r\n<br />\n依間藍到發黑<br />\n13好評 2負評<br />\n<br />\n有啲港豬見評價唔錯就會去食<br />\n<br />\n我哋就係要將呢啲全部負評爆燈<br />\n唔使理佢藍唔藍<br />\n最後黃定藍都唔會食<br />\n執笠收場<br />\n<br />\n希望本身有寫開OpenRice既手足幫幫手"},{"pid":"82a89eba62907dafe9fe19c600f502342d49997c","tid":1814624,"uid":335890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:44:54.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"bc97a523334d0f2f79a66ac3814622f8e8040c57","tid":1814624,"uid":335890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:45:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5ef6f4ecebeb1deb00b0ff6d4623d5a14bd2af0","tid":1814624,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:51:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}